name: Neurogen v1.1
description:
According to the tests, this model gives a very good detail of skin and textures. Great for close-up photorealistic portraits as well as various characters and models.

UPD 23.04.2023:

Neurogen Art release

UPD 26.03.2023:
v1.1: The new version has taken a step forward in the direction of versatility.

The detail of the half body planes and full body planes has been improved (don't forget to use the Hires fix). In addition to photorealism, you can use this model for digital art and anime as well. Texture detailing has been improved, and new colors have been added.

Prompt: portrait photo, close up, detailed face, detailed skin, raw,

The most important Trigger Words: close up, ultra macro

Euler A or DPM++ 2M Karras with 25 - 30 steps

CFG Scale: 4 - 5

CLIP skip: 1 or 2

modelVersions.name: v1.1
modelVersions.description:
The new version has taken a step forward in the direction of versatility.

The detail of the half body planes and full body planes has been improved (don't forget to use the Hires fix). In addition to photorealism, you can use this model for digital art and anime as well.

After fine-tuning, it was added:

- Better detail in textures and materials

- More saturated black. It's really dark at night now, don't forget the lighting :)

- The main innovation is the addition of new colors: carbon, douchrome and holographic. In order to use them, specify their names in the promt. If you like this update, I will add more unusual colors in the future.

Important: duochrome and holographic can have a strong effect on the picture as a whole, coloring unnecessary elements of the image. Experiment with the weight in Prompt to find the right value.

Note: If you want stronger contrast in your images, I recommend using VAE, which can be downloaded above by clicking the download button.
